comments.author: shasan
comments.body: Quote from: nanniandrea1991 on November 09, 2022, 09:15:11 AMWho knows an honest bet365 account seller?There are many "seller"...but many are thief!I would please reply from buyer.You should avoid any type of account buying from anyone. If you buy any account from anyone then you may face several problems:*The account can be restored*If the site requires any type of verification later then you can't verify thatIf you face a problem with the payment processor then you cant deposit or withdraw funds. To avoid all of these you should create an account for yourself or your family.
